        <p>Although Flare is a native Windows application, it is possible to run Flare on a Mac. This is possible through emulation programs such as Parallels, VMware, or Bootcamp.  Doing this makes it easy to boot Flare on the Windows partition.</p>
        <p>For more information, see this <a href="https://www.madcapsoftware.com/blog/can-i-run-madcap-flare-on-a-mac-oh-yes/" target="_blank">blog post</a>.</p>
